Achievements.Name: Perks of the Job

Achievements.Name: Tanking This Show On The Road

Achievements.Name: Got Lucky!
Achievements.Description: Kill a tank while your tank is immobile. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Sniper

Achievements.Name: Don't scratch the paint
Achievements.Description: Finish a match with 100% health with a potential damage taken of 1000 or more. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Tanks With Benefits

Achievements.Name: Absolute
Achievements.Description: Research a tier X tank.

Achievements.Name: Tactical Espionage

Achievements.Name: Now you see me...
Achievements.Description: Apply Camouflage to your tank.

Achievements.Name: This is World of Tanks
Achievements.Description: Be the last tank to be destroyed on your team. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Ranger
Achievements.Description: Destroy all enemy light tanks during a match, must be 3 or more. MP only.

Achievements.Name: The Sherminator

Achievements.Name: 'Tis But a Scratch
Achievements.Description: Win and survive a match with 3 or more damaged components. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Stand By Me
Achievements.Description: Survive and win a battle along with one or more platoon mates. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Top Operative
Achievements.Description: Complete 8 new operations.

Achievements.Name: Tanks ATTACKED
Achievements.Description: Complete mini-game.

Achievements.Name: Trebuchet!
Achievements.Description: Own 5 French Artillery Tanks simultaneously.

Achievements.Name: Conquering Ground
Achievements.Description: Win, survive and be one of the team

Achievements.Name: Not in MY House!
Achievements.Description: Destroy 2 enemy tanks trying to capture a friendly base. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Maximum Overdrive
Achievements.Description: Destroy 2 tanks by ramming them and survive. MP only.

Achievements.Name: First!
Achievements.Description: Be the first to destroy an enemy in a match on Highway or Steppes. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Coordination
Achievements.Description: Use the radial command menu to send a message from each category in a single match. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Japanese Connoisseur
Achievements.Description: Destroy 5 enemies each, of any nation, with 5 different Japanese tanks. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Right Where I Want You
Achievements.Description: Immobilize 100 enemies by destroying their treads. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Fire on Command
Achievements.Description: Destroy an enemy tank within 30 seconds of a team mate requesting fire on the enemy. MP only.

Achievements.Name: FTW!
Achievements.Description: Kill the last enemy alive or capture the flag for the win, 5 times. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Hero of the Day
Achievements.Description: Earn 20 or more ribbons in a single match (excluding the "Enemy Damaged!" ribbon). MP only.

Achievements.Name: Invader
Achievements.Description: Capture the maximum number of points from the enemy base, but not less than 80, 3 times. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Defender
Achievements.Description: Reduce the amount of enemy capture points on a friendly base by 70 or more, 3 times. MP only.

Achievements.Name: It Burns!
Achievements.Description: Set an enemy on fire twice within a single match. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Friends and Enemies
Achievements.Description: While in a platoon, destroy an enemy tank that is in a platoon. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Chinese Collection
Achievements.Description: Research a Light, Medium, and Heavy Chinese tank.

Achievements.Name: Boom Goes the Dynamite!
Achievements.Description: Destroy an enemy tank at full health with one shot. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Up to the Challenge
Achievements.Description: Win in four different Proving Grounds matches.

Achievements.Name: Under the Gun
Achievements.Description: Win in four different Proving Grounds matches with a tank that is tier VI or lower.

Achievements.Name: David and Goliath
Achievements.Description: Destroy a tank at least two tiers higher than your own. MP only.

Achievements.Name: My House Now!
Achievements.Description: Destroy two enemy tanks from within an enemy capture point. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Living on the Edge
Achievements.Description: Win a match with 5% or less health. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Murica
Achievements.Description: Destroy 4 enemy tanks in a single match while using an American tank. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Tank Ace
Achievements.Description: Earn the Ace Tanker Mastery Badge.

Achievements.Name: Let 'em have it
Achievements.Description: Destroy 2 different tanks with 2 different types of ammo in one match. MP only.

Achievements.Name: One Man Army
Achievements.Description: Earn 2x more XP than the 2nd best player on your team. MP only.

Achievements.Name: We Can Re-build Him
Achievements.Description: Repair 1,500 HP of damage on a tank after a single battle. MP only.

Achievements.Name: Death From Above
Achievements.Description: Land on or drive over an enemy, killing them. MP only.
